Directory: src/components
Purpose: React presentation components and UI views.
Responsibility: Renders the user controls, sidebars, settings sliders, node editor popups, and wraps the canvas elements for map rendering.
Key Files:
- MapView.tsx: Component holding the MapLibre GL instance, rendering vectors, routes, and points.
- Sidebar.tsx: Interface listing route analytics, settings, and node customization status.
- NodeEditor.tsx: Simple form for adding traffic light delays and tags.
